15 SUMMARY
1166 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, clarifies the
1177 applicability of federal law or regulation permitting the year-round observation of daylight
1188 time by striking the word "eastern" from the contingency provision in the bill describing
1199 federal law or regulation permitting the year-round observation of daylight saving time.
